it's one hour before the stores close. you might as well take me. i'm the last one who came along today,'' he said
dole trailed bush here in the polls by a substantial margin before dole won the iowa caucuses last monday. since then, he has surged in the polls, some of which gave him a small lead. but others suggested his surge had abated, leaving the race too close to call
william brock, dole's campaign manager, said that no matter what the outcome, bush was a loser in new hampshire. ``you can't have a campaign that collapses this fast and have any credibility,'' he said
while bush bid to salvage new hampshire, brock already was looking beyond
